{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"nonisolated","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"transaction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"_","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"transform","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"@escaping","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"inout"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Transaction","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Transaction","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore11TransactionV"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Void","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"View","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP"},{"text":"\n","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The transformation to apply to transactions"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"within this view."}]}],"name":"transform"}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Return Value","level":2,"anchor":"return-value"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A view that wraps this view and applies a transformation to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all transactions used within the view."}]}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Use this modifier to change or replace the animation used in a view.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Consider three identical animations controlled by a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"button that executes all three animations simultaneously:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The first animation rotates the “Rotation” "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text"},{"type":"text","text":" view by 360"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"degrees."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The second uses the "},{"code":"transaction(_:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" modifier to change the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"animation by adding a delay to the start of the animation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"by two seconds and then increases the rotational speed of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"“Rotation\\nModified” "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" view animation by a factor of 2."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The third animation uses the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"transaction(_:)"},{"text":" modifier to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"replace the rotation animation affecting the “Animation\\nReplaced”","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","isActive":true},{"text":" view with a spring animation.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The following code implements these animations:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["struct TransactionExample: View {","    @State private var flag = false","","    var body: some View {","        VStack(spacing: 50) {","            HStack(spacing: 30) {","                Text(\"Rotation\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees:","                                            self.flag ? 360 : 0))","","                Text(\"Rotation\\nModified\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees:","                                            self.flag ? 360 : 0))","                    .transaction { view in","                        view.animation =","                            view.animation?.delay(2.0).speed(2)","                    }","","                Text(\"Animation\\nReplaced\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees:","                                            self.flag ? 360 : 0))","                    .transaction { view in","                        view.animation = .interactiveSpring(","                            response: 0.60,","                            dampingFraction: 0.20,","                            blendDuration: 0.25)","                    }","            }","","            Button(\"Animate\") {","                withAnimation(.easeIn(duration: 2.0)) {","                    self.flag.toggle()","                }","            }","        }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this modifier on leaf views such as "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Image","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Button","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" rather"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"than container views such as "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/VStack","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/HStack","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":". The"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"transformation applies to all child views within this view; calling"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"transaction(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":" on a container view can lead to unbounded scope of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"execution depending on the depth of the view hierarchy."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"transaction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"((","kind":"text"},{"text":"inout","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore11TransactionV","text":"Transaction","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","text":"Void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP","text":"View","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"TransactionModifier.swift","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/OpenSwiftUIProject\/OpenSwiftUI\/blob\/main\/Sources\/OpenSwiftUICore\/Animation\/Transaction\/TransactionModifier.swift#L84"},"extendedModule":"OpenSwiftUICore","symbolKind":"method","externalID":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewPAAE11transactionyQryAA11TransactionVzcF::SYNTHESIZED::s:11OpenSwiftUI13EquatableViewV","title":"transaction(_:)","role":"symbol","platforms":[{"introducedAt":"13.0","deprecated":false,"name":"iOS","unavailable":false,"beta":false},{"introducedAt":"10.15","deprecated":false,"name":"macOS","unavailable":false,"beta":false},{"introducedAt":"13.0","deprecated":false,"name":"tvOS","unavailable":false,"beta":false},{"introducedAt":"1.0","deprecated":false,"name":"visionOS","unavailable":false,"beta":false},{"introducedAt":"6.0","deprecated":false,"name":"watchOS","unavailable":false,"beta":false}],"modules":[{"name":"OpenSwiftUI","relatedModules":["OpenSwiftUICore"]}]},"identifier":{"interfac